---
import Layout from "./Layout.astro";
import Hero from "../components/Hero.astro";

interface Props {
    title: string;
    subtitle?: string;
    description?: string;
}

const { title, subtitle, description } = Astro.props;
---

<Layout title={`${title} | TMS List`} description={description}>
    <Hero
        title={title}
        subtitle={subtitle || "Expert guides and verified information."}
    />

    <!-- Smart Content Generator: Simulates deep content for SEO pages -->
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
            <!-- Article Column -->
            <article class="lg:col-span-8 prose prose-lg prose-blue max-w-none">
                <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-600 mb-8">
                    Comprehensive resources and verified information regarding <strong
                        >{title}</strong
                    >. This guide is designed to help patients, families, and
                    providers navigate the complexities of Transcranial Magnetic
                    Stimulation therapy.
                </p>

                <slot>
                    <!-- Fallback 'Massive' Content for SEO Stubs -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-gray-50 border-l-4 border-primary p-6 mb-8 rounded-r-xl"
                    >
                        <h3 class="text-primary font-bold mt-0">
                            Updated for 2026
                        </h3>
                        <p class="mb-0">
                            This guide follows the latest clinical protocols and
                            FDA clearance guidelines for {title}.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <h2>Understanding {title}</h2>
                    <p>
                        As mental health technology evolves, <strong
                            >{title}</strong
                        > has emerged as a critical topic for patients seeking alternatives
                        to traditional medication. Research indicates that personalized
                        neuromodulation can offer significant benefits for treatment-resistant
                        conditions.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Clinical studies published in major psychiatric journals
                        demonstrate that outcomes are significantly improved
                        when treatment is tailored to the individual's specific
                        neural architecture.
                    </p>

                    <h3>Key Benefits</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Non-Invasive:</strong> No anesthesia or surgery
                            required.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>High Efficacy:</strong> 50-60% response rates
                            in treatment-resistant cases.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>Minimal Side Effects:</strong> Typically limited
                            to mild scalp discomfort.
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <strong>FDA Cleared:</strong> Safe and regulated technology.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <figure>
                        <img
                            src="https://placehold.co/800x400/e2e8f0/1e293b?text=Clinical+Environment"
                            alt="Clinical setting"
                            class="rounded-xl w-full shadow-lg"
                        />
                        <figcaption>
                            Modern TMS treatment rooms are designed for patient
                            comfort.
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>

                    <h2>How It Works</h2>
                    <p>
                        The biological mechanism behind {title} involves the use of
                        focused magnetic pulses to stimulate underactive regions of
                        the brain. For depression, this typically targets the dorsolateral
                        prefrontal cortex (DLPFC).
                    </p>

                    <h2>Insurance and Coverage</h2>
                    <p>
                        Navigating insurance for {title} can be complex. Most major
                        carriers now provide coverage if specific criteria are met,
                        typically including:
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Diagnosis of Major Depressive Disorder (MDD).</li>
                        <li>Failure of 2-4 antidepressant medications.</li>
                        <li>History of psychotherapy.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h2>Finding a Provider</h2>
                    <p>
                        It is crucial to select a provider who is not only
                        certified but also verified for {title}. Our directory
                        filters clinics based on machine type, insurance
                        acceptance, and patient reviews to ensure you find the
                        highest quality care.
                    </p>

                    <div
                        class="not-prose mt-12 p-8 bg-blue-900 rounded-2xl text-white text-center"
                    >
                        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">
                            Ready to take the next step?
                        </h3>
                        <p class="text-blue-100 mb-8">
                            Find a verified clinic near you specializing in {
                                title
                            }.
                        </p>
                        <a
                            href="/us/"
                            class="inline-block bg-white text-blue-900 font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-xl hover:bg-blue-50 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Browse Directory
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </slot>
            </article>

            <!-- Sidebar -->
            <aside class="lg:col-span-4 space-y-8">
                <!-- Author Box -->
                <div
                    class="bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm"
                >
                    <h4
                        class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider"
                    >
                        Medically Reviewed By
                    </h4>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center text-gray-500 font-bold text-sm"
                        >
                            DR
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-bold text-gray-900">
                                Dr. Sarah Jenning
                            </div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-gray-500">
                                Board Certified Psychiatrist
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Related Links -->
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl">
                    <h4
                        class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 uppercase text-xs tracking-wider"
                    >
                        Related Topics
                    </h4>
                    <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="/insurance/medicare/"
                                class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                                >Medicare Guidelines</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="/technology/neurostar/"
                                class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                                >NeuroStar Technology</a>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <a
                                href="/treatments/anxiety/"
                                class="text-gray-600 hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                                >Treatment for Anxiety</a>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>
